{txt}Statistics robust to heteroskedasticity{col 51}Prob > F{col 67}= {res}    0.1758
{txt}{col 51}R-squared{col 67}= {res}    0.0107
{txt}{col 51}Adj R-squared{col 67}= {res}   -0.0015
{txt}{col 51}Within R-sq.{col 67}= {res}    0.0044
{txt}{col 1}Number of clusters ({res}file_nbr{txt}) {col 30}= {res}       392{txt}{col 51}Root MSE{col 67}= {res}    0.9699

{txt}{ralign 78:(Std. err. adjusted for {res:392} clusters in {res:file_nbr})}
